#:*Instruction will be provided on how to handle difficult customers.
# That which instructs, or with which one is instructed; the intelligence or information [[impart]]ed; as: (a) [[Precept]]; [[information]]; [[teachings]]. (b) [[Direction]]; [[order]]; [[command]]. 
#*Shakespeare
#*:If my '''instructions''' may be your guide.

